HEADWORD: Tubing
<hw>Tub"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of
making tubes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A series of tubes; tubes, collectively; a length or
piece of a tube; material for tubes; <as>as, leather
<ex>tubing</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tubipora</ent>⟦br⟧
